1. *Glupost* je najgori oblik ponašanja. (Stupidity is the worst form of behaviour.)
2. On joj je dao izrazitu lekciju u pravu *gluposti*. (He gave her a harsh lesson in foolishness.)
3. Ona se zaklela da se nikad više neće ponašati u *glupostima*. (She swore she would never behave in foolishness again.)
4. Nećeš se izviniti zbog svoje *gluposti*. (You won't apologize for your foolishness.)
5. On je saopštio njegovu *glupost*. (He proclaimed his foolishness.)
6. Čini se da su njihove *gluposti* bile preterane. (It seems their foolishness was over the top.)